                <p>
                    <note place="foot" n="(2)" xml:id="fn1-2" prev="#fn1-1">
                        <hi rendition="#i">leghe quadrate di</hi> 20 <hi rendition="#i">al grado:
                            tutta l&#x2019;America ha</hi> 1,186,930<lb/>
                        <hi rendition="#i">di queste leghe, e</hi> 304,700 <hi rendition="#i"
                            >soltanto l&#x2019; Europa.</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rendition="#et">
